## Protocol.SystemInfo.GetInfoResponse.modelVersion property

A platform-dependent description of the version of the machine. On Mac OS, this is, for example, '10.1'. Will be the empty string if not supported.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
modelVersion: string;
```
